cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the application of deep neural networks for medical image segmentation, specifically for lateral ventricle segmentation in brain MR images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of pseudo-labels and their effectiveness in training the network, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of deep neural networks also falls under the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
